item.title: Ana add a quote by Marilyn Monroe
item.description: "I'm selfish, impatient and a little insecure. I make mistakes, I am out of control and at times hard to handle. But if you can't handle me at my worst, then you sure as hell don't deserve me at my best." -- Marilyn Monroe

item.title: Ana add a quote by Emily Dickinson
item.description: "Beauty is not caused. It is." -- Emily Dickinson

item.title: Ana add a quote by Henry David Thoreau
item.description: "I learned this, at least, by my experiment: that if one advances confidently in the direction of his dreams, and endeavors to live the life which he has imagined, he will meet with a success unexpected in common hours." -- Henry David Thoreau

item.title: Ana add a quote by Thomas A. Edison
item.description: "If we all did the things we are really capable of doing, we would literally astound ourselves." -- Thomas A. Edison

item.title: Ana add a quote by Robert Collier
item.description: "Success is the sum of small efforts, repeated day in and day out." -- Robert Collier

item.title: Ana add a quote by Arthur C. Clarke
item.description: "The only way of discovering the limits of the possible is to venture a little way past them into the impossible." -- Arthur C. Clarke
